리</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>Network</category> <description>IPIP와 WireGuard의 캡슐화·암호화 원리와 Noise_IK 핸드셰이크·cryptokey routing 차이를 비교표로 정리</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/wireguard-vs-ipip-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%90-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 23:22:40 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_created.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/wireguard-vs-ipip-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%90-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/20/wireguard-vs-ipip-차이점-정리.png" type="image/png" length="18843" /> </item> <item> <title>IPIP와 WireGuard 터널 직접 구성하고 비교하기</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>Network</category> <description>Docker 컨테이너 두 대에 IPIP·WireGuard 터널을 직접 올려 tcpdump로 평문·암호문을 대조하고 iperf3 처리량과 MTU까지 실측한 기록</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/ipip%EC%99%80-wireguard-%ED%84%B0%EB%84%90-%EC%A7%81%EC%A0%91-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EA%B3%A0-%EB%B9%84%EA%B5%90%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 23:22:40 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_created.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/ipip%EC%99%80-wireguard-%ED%84%B0%EB%84%90-%EC%A7%81%EC%A0%91-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EA%B3%A0-%EB%B9%84%EA%B5%90%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/20/ipip와-wireguard-터널-직접-구성하고-비교하기.png" type="image/png" length="17419" /> </item> <item> <title>GitOps와 ArgoCD 정리</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>DevOps</category> <description>GitOps 네 원칙과 ArgoCD 아키텍처, push·pull 모델 차이, 동기화 정책, Flux와의 비교까지 표로 정리</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/gitops%EC%99%80-argocd-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 23:22:40 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_created.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/gitops%EC%99%80-argocd-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/20/gitops와-argocd-정리.png" type="image/png" length="18672" /> </item> <item> <title>kind에 ArgoCD 올려 GitOps 동작 확인하기</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>DevOps</category> <description>kind 클러스터에 ArgoCD를 올려 guestbook을 sync하고, kubectl로 낸 drift가 selfHeal로 2초 만에 되돌아가는 과정과 롤백까지 실측한 기록</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/kind%EC%97%90-argocd-%EC%98%AC%EB%A0%A4-gitops-%EB%8F%99%EC%9E%91-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 23:22:40 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_created.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/kind%EC%97%90-argocd-%EC%98%AC%EB%A0%A4-gitops-%EB%8F%99%EC%9E%91-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/20/kind에-argocd-올려-gitops-동작-확인하기.png" type="image/png" length="20824" /> </item> <item> <title>컨테이너 내부 구조 정리</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>Docker</category> <description>namespace·cgroup부터 dockerd·containerd·runc 계층과 dockershim 제거, overlayfs, gVisor·Kata 런타임 선택지까지 표로 정리</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%84%88-%EB%82%B4%EB%B6%80-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 23:22:40 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_created.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%84%88-%EB%82%B4%EB%B6%80-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/20/컨테이너-내부-구조-정리.png" type="image/png" length="13292" /> </item> <item> <title>docker 없이 컨테이너 만들어보기</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>Docker</category> <description>docker 없이 unshare·cgroup·chroot·overlayfs·veth만으로 컨테이너를 손수 조립하고 20M 메모리 제한 OOM까지 실측한 기록</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/docker-%EC%97%86%EC%9D%B4-%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%84%88-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EC%96%B4%EB%B3%B4%EA%B8%B0/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 23:22:40 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_created.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/docker-%EC%97%86%EC%9D%B4-%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%84%88-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EC%96%B4%EB%B3%B4%EA%B8%B0/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/20/docker-없이-컨테이너-만들어보기.png" type="image/png" length="16060" /> </item> <item> <title>eBPF 정리</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>Linux</category> <description>eBPF의 verifier·JIT·maps·CO-RE 구조와 커널 모듈과의 차이, 훅 위치·개발 스택·Cilium·Falco 같은 대표 제품까지 정리</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/ebpf-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</link> <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 22:23:17 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_created.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/ebpf-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/20/ebpf-정리.png" type="image/png" length="14190" /> </item> <item> <title>bpftrace와 Cilium으로 eBPF 실습</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>Linux</category> <description>bpftrace와 Cilium으로 커널 추적과 서비스 네트워킹을 실측하고 strace 대비 이벤트당 약 2600배 낮은 오버헤드를 수치로 비교한 기록</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/bpftrace